    <a href="/{lang}/knowledge/network/usecases" class="btn-more tac fm small mb">Read all usecases &rarr;</a>

    <div class="hdr fm ttu mb" id="miners" name="miners">
      <h3><span>Be part of the network</span></h3>
    </div>
    <p class="normal mb--x2">If you are a miner or have spare computational power, DADI is a great application of your resource, delivering real world services for individuals, businesses and governments, whilst delivering income for you.</p>


    <div class="grid mb mb--x2">
      <div class="col w-1-3">
        <a href="/{lang}/knowledge/network/stargates" class="box bd bd-grey">
          <div class="box__inner">
            <h2 class="medium">Stargates</h2>
            <p class="normal">Provide domain routing and negotiate rates with Consumers.</p>
            <div class="box__footer">
              <span class="box__cta small fm color-tint">Learn more</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="col w-1-3">
        <a href="/{lang}/knowledge/network/gateways" class="box bd bd-grey">
          <div class="box__inner">
            <h2 class="medium">Gateways</h2>
            <p class="normal">Act as network aggregation points for Host capacity and negotiate rates with Hosts.</p>
            <div class="box__footer">
              <span class="box__cta small fm color-tint">Learn more</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="col w-1-3">
        <a href="/{lang}/knowledge/network/hosts" class="box bd bd-grey">
          <div class="box__inner">
            <h2 class="medium">Hosts</h2>
            <p class="normal">Provide processing power for multiple Consumer app bundles.</p>
            <div class="box__footer">
              <span class="box__cta small fm color-tint">Learn more</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-light-green pa fm read">
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="col w-1-2">
          <p><strong>Interested in becoming a Host or a Gateway?</strong> Register your interest and be the first to know when DADI starts accepting contributors to the network.</p>

          <p><strong>Want to run a Stargate?</strong> Email the team for more information stargates@dadi.co.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col w-1-2">
          <form action="https://daditech.createsend.com/t/i/s/alrdrt/" method="post"><input name="cm-name" id="fname" placeholder="Your name"><br><input name="cm-alrdrt-alrdrt" type="email" placeholder="Your email address"><br><button class="btn" type="submit">Submit</button></form>
        </div>
